<a title="專欄作者" href="https://gushi.tw/author-column/">專欄作者<i class="fa fa-angle-right fa-dropdown"></i></a></li> <li id="menu-item-48851" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-48851 menu-item-link"><a title="說書 SoBooks" href="https://sobooks.tw/">說書 SoBooks<i class="fa fa-angle-right fa-dropdown"></i></a></li> <li id="menu-item-33730" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-33730 menu-item-link"><a title="關於我們" href="https://gushi.tw/about/">關於我們<i class="fa fa-angle-right fa-dropdown"></i></a></li> </ul></div><div class="nav navbar-nav navbar-nav-last"><ul class="menu-smart sm menu-icons"><li class="menu-item-link social-icon tablet-hidden mobile-hidden social-177734"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/gushi.tw/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li><li class="menu-item-link search-icon style-light dropdown"><a href="#" class="trigger-overlay search-icon" data-area="search" data-container="box-container"> <i class="fa fa-search3"></i><span class="desktop-hidden"><span>搜尋</span></span><i class="fa fa-angle-down fa-dropdown desktop-hidden"></i> </a> <ul role="menu" class="drop-menu desktop-hidden"> <li> <form class="search" method="get" action="https://gushi.tw"> <input type="search" class="search-field no-livesearch" placeholder="搜尋…" value="" name="s" title="Search for:" /> </form> </li> </ul></li></ul></div><div class="desktop-hidden"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header></div><div class="main-wrapper"> <div class="main-container"> <div class="page-wrapper"> <div class="sections-container"><div id="page-header"><div class="header-wrapper header-uncode-block"> <div data-parent="true" class="collect_bigimg style-color-175272-bg row-container boomapps_vcrow"><div class="row no-top-padding no-bottom-padding no-h-padding row-slider row-parent row-header"><div class="owl-carousel-wrapper"><div class="uncode-slider owl-carousel-container"><div id="uslider_102366586" class="owl-carousel owl-element owl-dots-inside owl-height-forced" data-loop="true" data-autoheight="false" data-nav="true" data-dots="true" data-navspeed="400" data-autoplay="false" data-lg="1" data-md="1" data-sm="1"><div class="row-internal row-container boomapps_vcrow"><div class="row single-top-padding single-bottom-padding single-h-padding row-child limit-width" data-minheight="451"><div class="row-inner"><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-8 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode-single-media text-left"><div class="single-wrapper" style="max-width: 100%;"><a class="single-media-link" href="https://pressplay.cc/gushi.tw"><div class="tmb tmb-light tmb-media-first tmb-media-last tmb-content-overlay tmb-no-bg"> <div class="t-inside"><div class="t-entry-visual" tabindex="0"> <div class="t-entry-visual-tc"> <div class="uncode-single-media-wrapper"> <img src="https://gushi.tw/wp-content/uploads/gushi-1-2.png" width="700" height="459" alt=""></div></div></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-4 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode_text_column"><div class="pf-content"></p> <div class="in_collects"> <p class="pic"><img src="//gushi.tw/images/icon_col.png" alt="" width="34" height="34" /></p> <div class="title">故事會員招募中</div><div class="line"> </div><p>2014 年的 9 月，「故事：寫給所有人的歷史」正式登場。從那時開始，一直到今天，一千多個日子以來，感謝許許多多讀者朋友的支持。我們一步一步前進，而目標還在前方，所以我們希望和你一起，把故事繼續說下去！</p></div><p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-internal row-container boomapps_vcrow"><div class="row single-top-padding single-bottom-padding single-h-padding row-child limit-width" data-minheight="451"><div class="row-inner"><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-8 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode-single-media text-left"><div class="single-wrapper" style="max-width: 100%;"><a class="single-media-link" href="https://gushi.tw/portfolio/taipei/"><div class="tmb tmb-light tmb-media-first tmb-media-last tmb-content-overlay tmb-no-bg"> <div class="t-inside"><div class="t-entry-visual" tabindex="0"> <div class="t-entry-visual-tc"> <div class="uncode-single-media-wrapper"> <img src="https://gushi.tw/wp-content/uploads/%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8BBANNERHOME.jpg" width="796" height="495" alt=""></div></div></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-4 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode_text_column"><div class="pf-content"></p> <div class="in_collects"> <p class="pic"><img src="//gushi.tw/images/icon_col.png" alt="" width="34" height="34" /></p> <div class="title">臺北・故事</div><div class="line"> </div><p>臺北，是創作者的靈感之源，出現在琅琅上口的流行歌曲中，停留在文學家的筆墨中。從 1884 年建城以來，臺北的面貌一再轉變，臺北，是如何成為現在<wbr />的臺北呢？這是一座你以為很熟悉，卻不曾真正認識的城市。</p></div><p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-internal row-container boomapps_vcrow"><div class="row single-top-padding single-bottom-padding single-h-padding row-child limit-width" data-minheight="451"><div class="row-inner"><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-8 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode-single-media text-left"><div class="single-wrapper" style="max-width: 100%;"><a class="single-media-link" href="https://gushi.tw/portfolio/the-birth-of-modern-japan/"><div class="tmb tmb-light tmb-media-first tmb-media-last tmb-content-overlay tmb-no-bg"> <div class="t-inside"><div class="t-entry-visual" tabindex="0"> <div class="t-entry-visual-tc"> <div class="uncode-single-media-wrapper"> <img src="https://gushi.tw/wp-content/uploads/22496047_1945859835652347_3661469999721140713_o-1.jpg" width="1154" height="654" alt=""></div></div></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-4 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode_text_column"><div class="pf-content"></p> <div class="in_collects"> <p class="pic"><img src="//gushi.tw/images/icon_col.png" alt="" width="34" height="34" /></p> <div class="title">近代日本的形成</div><div class="line"> </div><p style="text-align: justify;">日本，離我們很近，也很遠。近代日本的形成過程中，充滿著來自不同文化與國家的人，透過他們，讓我們思考、理解近代日本的形成的多樣性與複雜性，同時看到台灣與東亞近代的進程。</p></div><p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-internal row-container boomapps_vcrow"><div class="row single-top-padding single-bottom-padding single-h-padding row-child limit-width" data-minheight="451"><div class="row-inner"><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-8 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode-single-media text-left"><div class="single-wrapper" style="max-width: 100%;"><a class="single-media-link" href="https://gushi.tw/portfolio/southeastasia/"><div class="tmb tmb-light tmb-media-first tmb-media-last tmb-content-overlay tmb-no-bg"> <div class="t-inside"><div class="t-entry-visual" tabindex="0"> <div class="t-entry-visual-tc"> <div class="uncode-single-media-wrapper"> <img src="https://gushi.tw/wp-content/uploads/banner%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9Ennn.jpg" width="796" height="495" alt=""></div></div></div></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pos-top pos-center align_left column_child col-lg-4 boomapps_vccolumn single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell boomapps_vccolumn no-block-padding"><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode_text_column"><div class="pf-content"></p> <div class="in_collects"> <p class="pic"><img src="//gushi.tw/images/icon_col.png" alt="" width="34" height="34" /></p> <div class="title">不是誰的他方：東南亞故事</div><div class="line"> </div><p style="text-align: justify;">從移工到新住民，從出國旅行到南向政策，臺灣與鄰近的東南亞，互動越來越密切了。但是，除了華人移居、西方殖民以及現代東協的統合，關於這些國家，你還能夠說出多少故事？東南亞不是誰的「他方」，每個國家都有自己的歷史，只等待你看見。</p></div><p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><center><ins class="clickforceads" style="display:inline-block;width:728px;height:90px;" data-ad-zone="4861"></ins></center></div><article id="post-33735" class="page-body style-color-175272-bg post-33735 page type-page status-publish hentry">
